  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction to GNOME Font Viewer</title>

    <para>
      The <application>GNOME Font Viewer</application> package contains
      font viewer for the <application>GNOME</application> Desktop.
    </para>

    &lfs70_checked;

